casebody.data:
175 A.3d 175 DEXTER & KILCOYNE, ESQS., PLAINTIFFS-RESPONDENTS, v. ANTHONY X. ARTURI, JR., ESQ. AND ARTURI, D'ARGENIO, GUAGLARDI & MELITI, LLP, DEFENDANTS-PETITIONERS.

C-368 September Term 2017

080113 November 29, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004862-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
